longBusinessSummary: Qatari German Company for Medical Devices (Q.P.S.C.) manufactures and sells single use disposable syringes in the Middle East. The company offers Q JectUltra, an insulin syringe serving as a tool in diabetic care; Q Flow for infusion therapy; Q Need, a single use hypodermic needle; Q Ject, a single use syringe for the curative medications; and Q Safe, a re-use prevention syringe. It also trades in medical equipment, tools, and supplies. Qatari German Company for Medical Devices (Q.P.S.C.) was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Doha, Qatar.
